# ConvertMyStuff Project Mission

ConvertMyStuff.com is a public, SEO-focused converter, calculator, generator, and utility tools platform.

The primary product is fast, useful, indexable public tool pages that work without login.

Do not build this as a login-first SaaS dashboard.

Normal public users must be able to use basic tools without creating an account.

Optional account features may be added later for:
- saved history
- favorite tools
- saved settings
- saved projects
- batch processing
- larger file limits
- API access
- no-ad experience
- branded exports
- billing
- admin management

